Top Nollywood act that include Tina Mba, Nobert Young, Nancy Isime, Broda Shaggi, Omotunde Adebowale-David, Bucci Franklin, and Instagram sensation, Lasisi Elenu amongst others have featured in upcoming  comedy movie ‘ The Razz Guy’ which was originally shot in 2019. Coming from the stable of the makers of the critically acclaimed ‘Sylvia’ movie; this new project is directed by Udoka Oyeka. ‘The Razz Guy’ follows the story of an arrogant lawyer who loses his ability to speak proper English after a spell is cast on him.